SELECT /* TODO: 컬럼 명시 필요 */ * FROM ( SELECT ROWNUM RN , TB.* FROM ( SELECT /* TODO: 컬럼 명시 필요 */ * FROM ( SELECT A.BBS_ID , B.BBS_NM , A.TRGET_ID , D.USER_NM , A.REGIST_SE_CODE , C.CODE_NM AS REGIST_SE_CODE_NM , A.USE_AT , A.FRST_REGISTER_ID , A.FRST_REGIST_PNTTM FROM TB_BBS_USE A LEFT OUTER JOIN TB_BBS_MASTER B ON A.BBS_ID = B.BBS_ID LEFT OUTER JOIN TB_CMMN_DETAIL_CODE C ON C.CODE = A.REGIST_SE_CODE LEFT OUTER JOIN VW_USER_MASTER D ON A.TRGET_ID = D.ESNTL_ID WHERE A.BBS_ID IN ( SELECT BBS_ID FROM TB_BBS_USE WHERE TRGET_ID = #{trgetId} AND USE_AT = 'Y' ) AND A.REGIST_SE_CODE = 'REGC07' UNION ALL SELECT A.BBS_ID , B.BBS_NM , A.TRGET_ID , '[전체]' USER_NM , A.REGIST_SE_CODE , C.CODE_NM AS REGIST_SE_CODE_NM , A.USE_AT , A.FRST_REGISTER_ID , A.FRST_REGIST_PNTTM FROM TB_BBS_USE A LEFT OUTER JOIN TB_BBS_MASTER B ON A.BBS_ID = B.BBS_ID LEFT OUTER JOIN TB_CMMN_DETAIL_CODE C ON C.CODE = A.REGIST_SE_CODE WHERE A.BBS_ID IN ( SELECT BBS_ID FROM TB_BBS_USE WHERE TRGET_ID = #{trgetId} ) AND A.REGIST_SE_CODE IN ('REGC05', 'REGC06') UNION ALL SELECT A.BBS_ID , B.BBS_NM , CASE WHEN E.EMPLYR_ID IS NULL THEN F.EMPLYR_ID ELSE E.EMPLYR_ID END AS TRGET_ID , CASE WHEN G.USER_NM IS NULL THEN H.USER_NM ELSE G.USER_NM END AS USER_NM , 'REGC07' AS REGIST_SE_CODE , '게시판사용자등록' AS REGIST_SE_CODE_NM , '' AS USE_AT , '' AS FRST_REGISTER_ID , SYSDATETIME AS FRST_REGIST_PNTTM FROM TB_BBS_USE A LEFT OUTER JOIN TB_BBS_MASTER B ON A.BBS_ID = B.BBS_ID LEFT OUTER JOIN TB_CMMN_DETAIL_CODE C ON C.CODE = A.REGIST_SE_CODE LEFT OUTER JOIN TB_CMMNTY_USER E ON E.CMMNTY_ID = #{trgetId} LEFT OUTER JOIN TB_CLUB_USER F ON F.CLB_ID = #{trgetId} LEFT OUTER JOIN VW_USER_MASTER G ON E.EMPLYR_ID = G.ESNTL_ID LEFT OUTER JOIN VW_USER_MASTER H ON F.EMPLYR_ID = H.ESNTL_ID WHERE A.BBS_ID IN ( SELECT BBS_ID FROM TB_BBS_USE WHERE TRGET_ID = #{trgetId} AND USE_AT = 'Y' ) AND A.REGIST_SE_CODE IN ('REGC05', 'REGC06') AND ( (A.BBS_ID, E.EMPLYR_ID) NOT IN (SELECT BBS_ID, TRGET_ID FROM TB_BBS_USE) OR (A.BBS_ID, F.EMPLYR_ID) NOT IN (SELECT BBS_ID, TRGET_ID FROM TB_BBS_USE) ) ) TT
WHERE TT.USER_NM LIKE '%' || #{searchWrd} || '%'
ORDER BY TT.USER_NM DESC ) TB ) Z WHERE RN BETWEEN #{firstIndex} + 1 AND #{firstIndex} + #{recordCountPerPage}

